name: Fornax Void - Hochwyr the Alchemist
description: It was one of those nights again: high up in the mountains, hidden in his tower, Hochwyr the Alchemist was searching for an elixir, able to relive him of the curse of being horned, which ruined his career as an opera singer and beard model and later even lead to his exclusion from the the local yodel club. ◢◤ 256 colors, 15 frames, 270p native upscaled to 2160p. ◢◤ Music recorded with the Roland JV-2080 equipped with the SR-JV80-15 Special FX Collection sound expansion board.
